<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 13 at 8:00AM EST  by NWS New York City - Upton</headline>
<description>...PATCHY DENSE FOG THIS MORNING...
Areas of fog have developed this morning. There are some patches
of dense fog where visibilities will be reduced to a quarter mile
or less.
Motorists should proceed with extra caution this morning and be
prepared for rapidly changing visibilities. Slow down, leave extra
room between vehicles and use low beam headlights.</description>
